Phrase: It has been about a week since the opening of the Metro Hole. The Special Steel Squad was given a new mission to investigate Iris Metro and to cooperate with its Allied Forces.

The theory that the two universes are connected via the existence of the five Giant Trees is currently strong, and it is believed that if the anomalies occurring underground are not resolved, there will be major repercussions on the surface too.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: We were not officially mobilised until cooperation was established between our two universes. We have received reports from the Headquarters of the Metro Allied Forces that both Miss Versailles and Miss Miyako, who had gone to investigate this castle in question, had not yet returned to their posts. In response, we were sent via the Mist Train to conduct a search and rescue operation.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Incidentally, the rear unit on standby at the outpost were stranded due to a Phantom Mist manifested along the way, but we of the SSS had eliminated the source of the Mist and are now back in position.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: It was just as I thought. We were worried when we didn't get any help.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: We of the SSS have travelled downwards to Metro and has taken all possible precautions. We will henceforth assist you to investigate this castle. Miss Versailles, we will like to request your help again to assist the SSS.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Of course. Miyako and I are still ready to fight.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: On the contrary, please meet up with the rear unit, Miyako.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Eh?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Miyako cannot fight with Yoshino and friends. You have to join another unit and do other jobs.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Why? I was looking forward to fighting with Yoshino-chan together...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yes, Yoshino was looking forward to it too.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Then I can stay with you together, right?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: No, we can't.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Why not?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Well, umm...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: ...No, can't do it, can't do it!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Oui oui~! Yoshino did her best~♪ Leave this to us big sisters here, okay~?

Name: Putra
Phrase: I-I think you did better than you did in practice, I gueeess~?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: While we talk with her, you should go and play with Yakutsk, alright~?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: ...Munen. Preparation is not kanpen.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: There she goes.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Aiyoh, you're sloppy, beast ears.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Umm, uh...

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Ah, désolé~? Yoshino seems to get nervous in front of Miyako for some reason.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Well, she's not that good at talking to begin with...

Name: Putra
Phrase: Yeah yeah. The whole time we were on the Train, she kept saying, 'Yoshino's going to have lots of talks with Miyako!', just so you know?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I see? She doesn't have to be so nervous...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: So why do I have to move to the rear?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: When she said to move to rear, she meant that the M. Nishiki Railway Army wants Miyako to hurry up at base in an emergency.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Don't tell me, there's a celestial anomaly in M. Nishiki too...

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: We haven't heard any details, but I did see some of the strongest people in M. Nishiki gathered at the Allied base.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Maybe it's time to repay the price for sending so many people to M. St. Iris's Metro Hole.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: You get over there now, Miyako. Leave the rest to me.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Versailles...

Name: Versailles
Phrase: You are a member of my unit, Miyako. But you are also a soldier of M. Nishiki. As a citizen and soldier of M. Nishiki, you have to battle for your country.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I understand it's a difficult time for the Allied Forces, right? But the only ones left in the Versailles Corps is just me and you now, are you sure?

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Don't worry, I'm not alone. I'm together with the SSS and Conductor. Everything will be fine.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Besides, this is an order from the Allied High Command. Miyako has no authority to disobey.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes, that's true, but...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Please be really careful, listen to what Conductor-san says, okay?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Don't go running off on your own, don't try to force your way through with horrible acting, and don't be reckless.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: I won't do that.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: You're strong, Versailles, but you have a short temper, so it's easy for you to get worked up, you know? I can handle you fine, but you mustn't cause trouble for the SSS, got it?

Name: Versailles
Phrase: I-I know that much! Stop saying embarrassing things of me in front of everyone.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I'm worried.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Hmm hmm... if anything, Miyako is the one who holds the reins, isn't she? Looks difficult for her in many ways?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Not necessarily? Some girls like to be up close and personal.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Really?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: That's just the way it is. Especially towards someone you like.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Hmmmmmmm...

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Excuse me. I have been informed that I have other orders. I will join the rear unit and return to the base. Please help me take care of Versailles, SSS.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: My pleasure, Miss. Please leave the rest to us.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Iris Cloud's finest Divine Child will clear the rain clouds over this castle.

Name: Victoria
Phrase: And the name of that Child is...

Name: Victoria
Phrase: Paddington Elrond!

Name: Paddington
Phrase: ...Eh? Is that me!?

Name: Victoria
Phrase: So long as Lady Paddington and I are here, we will not allow evil to exist. We will clear away all the Phantom Mist that manifests upon this world, that threatens the iridescent clouds.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Oh, and also! Because Sir Conductor and the rest of us will fight with everything we've got!

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Yes, of course! Let's all work together to clear this Mist!

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Miss Miyako, that is why you shouldn't worry about us, and go on to your next mission.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes, thank you very much. Please be careful, everyone.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Goodbye, Yoshino-chan. Let's talk again next time we meet, shall we?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Umm, yes! Next time!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Have a safe trip.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Mhm, Be careful, Yoshino-chan.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Why are you hiding behind me? You look more scared than nervous.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: 'Ughhhhh... Yoshino couldn't do it.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: What a bother, you were so talkative on the train too.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino was able to do it because I practiced with Yakky-tan. Yoshino couldn't do it with the real Miyako.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: It's just that Yoshino's stomach is churning.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Then write down what you want to say on a piece of paper so that next time you can speak properly.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Because there are things that you THINK you could say the next time you see them, but you weren't able to just say them directly.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: You're right...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Yoshino will do the best. Next time we meet, will do my best not to cognac.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: You mean 'panic', not 'cognac'.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Ooooh- that's what it is. Yoshino got 'panic' jumbled up with 'konran'.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Thank you, Yakky-tan. Thanks to you, Yoshino is better. Will let you touch my tail again tonight.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: ...Geez, you're quite cute in your own way.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: ...It's love.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: HAAAAAAAAAAHH-!?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: L-L-LOVE!? Of course not, I'm not in love with her!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: What? Not referring to you, Yakutsk.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: I'm talking about Yoshino, she loves Miyako♪

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Y-Yes I agree! Yoshino is crazy about Miyako. I-I've never been... in love before, so I don't know much about it.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: But let's not make fun of her. I'm sure you know why Yoshino is so interested in her, right?

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: Well, oui. I have an inkling.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Then we shouldn't make any more noise than we have to. She likes Miyako and wants to get to know her. Let's pretend that's all we know right now.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: She will. I'll reflect a little myself.

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: But you know, sometimes things do get strange.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Where there are farewells, there are encounters. Travel long enough and these things can happen too.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Now, let's get to work as soon as possible!
